description:
This is our classic Speed Dating event where you will have up to 20 dates each lasting between 4 and 5 minutes. Please arrive promptly for registration where you will be checked in, given your Date card and name badge. Then when everyone arrives you spend approximately two hours of fun chatting and dating. There will usually be a 15 minute break half way through the evening to refresh your drinks etc.
Perfectly located on Bristol's Harbourside, you can't miss us! And you wouldn't want to. With eclectic and unusual furniture over two floors, you're spoilt for choice with places to sit. MySpeedDate have exclusive use of the 2nd floor for these events, a perfect venue with plenty of room and comfort for the most relaxing experience.

http://www.myspeeddate.co.uk/event_details.php?event=563
title: Speed Dating-26 - 38 (Guideline only)
